---
title: Chop House Steaks and Creamy Mushrooms with Potatoes, Bacon and Chive Goat Cheese
description: This steakhouse dinner is simple, juicy and luxurious! Pan-seared steaks are smothered with delectable creamy mushrooms and crisp roasted potatoes are topped with creamy chive goat cheese and bacon. Snap peas bring a bit of green to finish of a plate of amazing tastes.
